OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUse words carefully warns  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FJenrick after migrant row  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Immigration Minister Robert Jenrick has
OL,6, said politicians must choose their     
OL,7, words "carefully" after a Holocaust    
OL,8, survivor criticised the home           
OL,9, secretary's language on immigration.   
OL,11,FOn Friday, Joan Salter, 83, told Suella
OL,12,FBraverman her words reminded her of    
OL,13,Flanguage used to "justify the murder of
OL,14,Fmy family and millions of others".     
OL,16,FMr Jenrick told ITV it was right to    
OL,17,Flisten to Ms Salter's experiences.     
OL,19,FHowever, he also said Ms Braverman had 
OL,20,Fmade an "important" point.             
